<div class="story">
<p>Schooner Ridge is one of the more modern subdivisions in Duck consisting of 91 building lots. Each lot is large enough to hold a large house with an in ground pool. There is an active home owners association with an HOA fee to cover the maintenance of the private roads, the indoor pool, racquetball court, tennis court, playground, health club, clubhouse and ocean front out door pool. There is some limited ocean side parking close to the ocean front.</p>
  <p>Schooner Ridge is located in the heart of downtown <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/" title="Duck">Duck</a> and all of the shops and restaurants are in walking distance. You can find Schooner Ridge just past the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/duck-landing.asp" title="Duck Landing">Duck Landing</a>  and before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/poteskeet-village.asp" title="Poteskeet Village">Poteskeet Village</a>. </p>
